<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٤٧٧ - حَدَّثَنَا غُنْدَرٌ، عَنْ شُعْبَةَ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ وَضَّاحٍ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ قَتَادَةَ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«يُعِيدُ سَجْدَتَيِ السَّهْوِ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>